<%= breadcrumbs_from(@root) -%>

<h1>Git access to the wiki</h1>
<p>
  The project wiki is a Git repository containing Markdown formatted
  pages. You can clone the repository, and if you have access to it,
  you may even make local changes and push them to Gitorious.
</p>

<p><strong>The Git URL to this wiki is:</strong></p>
<% if logged_in? &&  @project.wiki_repository.wiki_writable_by?(current_user) -%>
  <p><pre>git clone <%= writable_wiki_url(@project) -%></pre></p>
<% else -%>
  <p><pre>git clone <%= regular_wiki_url(@project) -%></pre></p>
<% end -%>



<% content_for :sidebar do -%>
  <%= render :partial => "actions" -%>
<% end -%>
